#: templates/property/scpi_investment_form.html:66
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The <strong>bare ownership ratio</strong> is the percentage "
"of the full share value attributed to bare ownership at the time of purchase "
"(e.g. 65%% if you paid 65%% of the share price for the bare ownership). The "
"estimated value increases linearly to 100%% by the dismemberment end date.\n"
"              "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                La <strong>quote-part de nue-propriété</strong> est le "
"pourcentage de la valeur de la part attribué à la nue-propriété lors de "
"l'acquisition (ex. 65%% si vous avez payé 65%% du prix de la part pour la "
"nue-propriété). La valeur estimée progresse linéairement jusqu'à 100%% à la "
"date de fin du démembrement.\n"
"              "

